Onevent BEFORE_INPUT Call AS_SIMDET(zc) From W1ITC1
Onevent INIT_AREA Call D_SIMDET(zc) From W1ITC1
Return

Subprog D_SIMDET(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
If varinit([M]SIMDET,indice)=0
 VALEUR = "152"
